{"tid":94031,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ADATA SSD","createTime":"2017-01-25T01:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T09:10:35.000Z","uid":77334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d35c3571875da678bb921ab1510feaefa9770fd4","tid":94031,"uid":77334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"昨天發現SSD壞左，用左一年左右，用用下部機好慢，之後發現event viewer 有bad sector, 即刻換另一隻SSD, clone返個windows時會出read error, 但可以ignore佢，最後clone完出來嘜事都冇！<br />\n<br />\n隻SSD插落第二部機暫時冇事，adata個tools又顯示health! 打去代理問！問佢點check是否壞左，如果唔係壞我唔拿來整，代理居然答我好簡單的，你自己去google一下睇下點check! 聽完我就即刻著左，你對user既基本支援嘜都冇，我唔check拿過來整，咁你點check, 佢答我你拿過來我都唔會睇，我直接寄返廠，整好先叫你返來取！<br />\n<br />\n請問其他師兄用邊隻牌子好售後服務支援好！例如係佢地一兩日內會check真係壞就換隻新既俾你呢？<br />\n<br />\n我個情況如果自己check用嘜野軟件check好？"},{"pid":"d2b7c43c578d205352b4a5330f246a8e22721477","tid":94031,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"巴打你用咩型號SSD？代理係咪聯強？"},{"pid":"e65d9eab2c22f2aa309350edff62497a41dea247","tid":94031,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"又係adata，唔明點解咁伏都仲咁多人買"},{"pid":"2362edf4dd8749965abd0c601dd51bfdf4bfa77d","tid":94031,"uid":77334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你用咩型號SSD？代理係咪聯強？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係聯強買的，作天我先打俾Adata, 佢地俾呢個電話我2893-6289，就係得到上面結果，我今日打去問Synnex, 佢叫我填RMA form來收！"},{"pid":"246a3323efbcc6596426305787d6d984d1620bd4","tid":94031,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"對我黎講<br />\n唔會壞=好售後"},{"pid":"e93fe5475d93ebdb599ce0e5925516ee3029c542","tid":94031,"uid":24863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對我黎講<br />\n唔會壞=好售後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f89f83ca8781ef31577fddba7e5db363eba587","tid":94031,"uid":73177,"like"